        <description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m one of the co-founders of &lt;a href=&#34;https://hubblo.org&#34;&gt;Hubblo&lt;/a&gt;, a consulting and a study office specialized in environmental, climate, social and societal effects of the tech industry. In this position, I work especially on topics related to Datacenters, AI, Cloud services and wider ICT infrastrctures.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m also an active contributor to the &lt;a href=&#34;https://boavizta.org&#34;&gt;Boavizta&lt;/a&gt; non-profit, in which I contribute to digital commons helping organizations and individuals to better understand, evaluate and reduce the environmental impacts of digital services.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
